Thanks Zedites

The following is most useful for solving the "What was the name of the file 
I created/modified recently somewhere in this hierarchy" problem

# list 5 most recent files in hierarchy
ls -lt **/*.tex(D.om[1,5]) 


# variation with paging

ls -lt **/*.tex(D.om) | more



